<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Canceled</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #00466a;">Xuthority</h2>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em;">
            Hi <%= userName %>,
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold;">
            üö´ Subscription Canceled
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            We're sorry to see you go! Your <strong><%= planName %></strong> subscription has been successfully canceled as requested.
        </p>

        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #721c24;">
                üìã Cancellation Details:
            </p>
            <div style="color: #666;">
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Plan:</strong> <%= planName %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Canceled On:</strong> <%= canceledDate %></p>
                <% if (accessUntilDate) { %>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Access Until:</strong> <%= accessUntilDate %></p>
                <% } %>
                <% if (cancelReason) { %>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= cancelReason %></p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <% if (accessUntilDate) { %>
        <div style="background-color: #d1ecf1; border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #0c5460; font-weight: bold;">
                ‚ÑπÔ∏è Important Information
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #0c5460;">
                You'll continue to have access to your premium features until <strong><%= accessUntilDate %></strong>. After that date, your account will automatically switch to our free plan.
            </p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            <strong>What happens next:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul style="font-size: 1em; color: #666; margin-left: 20px;">
            <li>No further charges will be made to your payment method</li>
            <li>You'll receive a confirmation receipt for this cancellation</li>
            <% if (accessUntilDate) { %>
            <li>You can continue using premium features until <%= accessUntilDate %></li>
            <li>After <%= accessUntilDate %>, you'll have access to our free features</li>
            <% } else { %>
            <li>Your account has been switched to our free plan</li>
            <% } %>
            <li>All your data and account information remain safe with us</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #856404; font-weight: bold;">
                üí° Changed Your Mind?
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #856404;">
                You can reactivate your subscription anytime! Just visit your account settings and choose a plan that works for you.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" 
               style="background-color: #00466a; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 10px;">
                Go to Dashboard
            </a>
            <a href="<%= reactivateUrl %>" 
               style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
                Reactivate Subscription
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            <strong>We'd Love Your Feedback</strong><br>
            Your feedback helps us improve our service. If you have a moment, we'd appreciate knowing what led to your decision to cancel. You can reply to this email or contact us at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #00466a;"><%= supportEmail %></a>.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            Thank you for being part of the Xuthority community. We hope to serve you again in the future!
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            Best regards,<br>
            The Xuthority Team
        </p>

        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 10px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #aaa;">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><%= companyAddress %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 